"MacGyver"
Halloween Knights (1989)

Original Air Date:
30 October 1989 (Season 5, Episode 6)

Plot Summary:
MacGyver's nemesis Murdoc returns, but this time to strike a deal with his enemy. Murdoc's sister is going to be killed by Murdoc's former employers...
This is a 48 Minute episode, no need for nearly 3GB.
